# 🧠 OS Concept 1: Real-Time Systems

## 1️⃣ Simple Idea

A real-time system must respond:

👉 within a strict time limit.

Correctness depends on:

✔ output
✔ timing

---

## 🧠 Real-World Analogy

Airbag system in car 🚗

If response comes after 5 seconds:

❌ useless

Must respond immediately.

---

# Types of Real-Time Systems

---

## 🔹 Hard Real-Time

Missing deadline = system failure

Examples:

* aircraft control
* medical devices

---

## 🔹 Soft Real-Time

Delay acceptable but undesirable

Examples:

* video streaming
* gaming

---

## 🎯 Placement Question

**Q: Difference between hard and soft real-time systems?**

👉 Hard real-time cannot miss deadlines, soft real-time can tolerate small delays.

---

## 🧠 Memory Trick

```text id="6r2y7k"
Hard = strict deadline
Soft = flexible deadline
```

